---
title: Cashflow — Registrar lançamento (POST /ledger/api/v1/entries)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Merchant as Merchant (terminal POS)
    participant GW as Gateway (YARP)
    participant API as Ledger.Api
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant OUT as Outbox dispatcher (MassTransit)
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ
    participant WRK as Consolidation.Worker
    participant CACHE as Redis (cache)
    participant MGO as MongoDB

    Merchant->>+GW: POST /ledger/api/v1/entries<br/>Bearer JWT + Idempotency-Key
    GW->>GW: Valida JWT (cache JWKS 5min)
    GW->>GW: Rate-limit sliding window<br/>(entry-write-policy 30/s/merchant)
    GW->>+API: Proxy → POST /api/v1/entries<br/>X-Correlation-Id, traceparent
    API->>API: IdempotencyKeyEndpointFilter (header check)
    API->>API: RegisterEntryCommand → ValidationBehavior

    rect rgb(245, 245, 250)
    note over API,DB: TX única — entry + outbox + idempotency_key
        API->>+DB: BEGIN
        API->>DB: INSERT entries (id Guid v7, ...)
        API->>DB: INSERT idempotency_keys (merchant_id, key) UNIQUE
        API->>DB: INSERT messaging.OutboxMessage (EntryRegisteredV1)
        API->>DB: COMMIT
        DB-->>-API: OK
    end

    API-->>-GW: 201 Created<br/>{id, status: "Confirmed", ...}
    GW-->>-Merchant: 201 Created

    note over OUT,MQ: Após o commit, dispatcher polleia OutboxMessage<br/>(SKIP LOCKED, QueryDelay 1s)
    OUT->>+DB: SELECT ... FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED
    DB-->>-OUT: pending rows
    OUT->>+MQ: BasicPublish Cashflow.Contracts.V1:EntryRegisteredV1
    MQ-->>-OUT: ack
    OUT->>DB: UPDATE OutboxMessage SET delivered

    MQ->>+WRK: Deliver EntryRegisteredV1
    WRK->>WRK: UseMessageRetry exp 5x (em caso de transient error)
    WRK->>+MGO: FindOneAndUpdate filter:{merchantId, date, $ne LastEventId}<br/>$inc totals + $set lastEventId
    MGO-->>-WRK: upsert / no-op (idempotente)
    WRK-->>-MQ: ack

    note over CACHE: Próximo GET /balances/.../daily<br/>hit cache stale por até 60s (TTL).<br/>Mecanismo cache aside lê do Mongo no miss.
